    "chemicalDescription": [
      "sh-Oligopeptide-1 sr-Ocean Pout Oligopeptide-1 Dipeptide-39  is a single chain recombinant protein produced by fermentation in  E. coli. The starting gene is synthesized by the fusion of the gene from sh-Oligopeptide-1 and sr-Ocean Pout Polypeptide-1 and Dipeptide-39. The fusion protein contains 118 amino acids which may contain disulfide bonds and/or glycosylation, and consists of the proper sequence of the 20 standard amino acids."
